   <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://masterpro.ws" target="_blank"><img style="margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;" src="/modules/mod_jweather_by_ip/img/logo.png" alt="Masterpro.ws" /></a></p>
<p><strong>jWeather by ip</strong></p>
<p>The module <strong>jWeather by ip</strong> allows you to choose between WorldWeatherOnline and OpenWeatherMap, and between IPGeolocation.io, REST API SypexGeo and binary file SypexGeo. SypexGeo distributed under the BSD license, it is absolutely free.</p>
<p>Starting from v.1.9, jWeatherByIP is includes the ability to show the weather on the Google Map.</p>
<p>Each user without registering gets a 10 000 requests per month to REST API (identification by IP). When you register (it's free) on the site is given a unique key for accounting requests, as well as at the expense of added bonus requests (30 000 per month).</p>
<p><strong>Getting Started, step by step:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Install module.</li>
<li>Go to <a href="https://worldweatheronline.com/developer" target="_blank">World Weather Online</a> and get your premium api_key. Attention, World Weather Online Free API signup has now been suspended. For new users to use Weather API they will be issued Premium Trial key for free testing for 60 days.</li>
<li>Optional: you can use <a href="https://home.openweathermap.org/users/sign_up" target="_blank">OpenWeatherMap</a> weather station.</li>
<li>Optional: go to <a href="https://sypexgeo.net/ru/download/" target="_blank">Sypexgeo.net</a> and download Sypex Geo City UTF-8 (or <a href="https://sypexgeo.net/files/SxGeoCity_utf8.zip" target="_blank">direct link</a>). Unzip the file. You must move SxGeoCity.dat to the directory module - /public_html/modules/mod_jweather_by_ip/ .</li>
<li>Optional: go to <a href="https://sypexgeo.net/ru/pc/auth/" target="_blank">Sypex Geo</a> and get your free (or Premium) api_key.</li>
<li>Optional: go to <a href="https://app.ipgeolocation.io/auth/login" target="_blank">IPGeolocation.io</a> and get your free (or Premium) api_key.</li>
<li>Go to "Module Manager" ->  "jWeather by ip", enter your api_keys, select the required options and turn on the module.</li>
<li>Enjoy!</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="http://masterpro.ws/jweather-by-ip-pogoda-po-ip-dlya-joomla" target="_blank">Learn more at <strong>the Weather by ip</strong> project website.</a></p>
<p><strong>jWeather by ip</strong> module is released under the <a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html" target="_blank">GNU/GPL license.</a></p>]]></description>
   <updateservers>
      <server type="extension" priority="1" name="Masterpro project">https://masterpro.ws/geo/updates/jweather.xml</server>
   </updateservers>
   <files>
      <filename module="mod_jweather_by_ip">mod_jweather_by_ip.php</filename>
      <filename module="mod_jweather_by_ip">helper.php</filename>
      <filename>mod_jweather_by_ip.xml</filename>
      <folder>src</folder>
      <folder>img</folder>
      <folder>tmpl</folder>
   </files>
   <languages folder="language">
      <language tag="en-GB">en-GB.mod_jweather_by_ip.ini</language>
      <language tag="ru-RU">ru-RU.mod_jweather_by_ip.ini</language>
   </languages>
   <config>
      <fields name="params">
         <fieldset name="basic">
            <field name="google_map" type="radio" default="0" label="GOOGLEMAP" description="GOOGLEMAP_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="20">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field type="spacer" hr="true" />
            <field name="api_choose" type="list" default="1" label="Select API" description="CHOOSE_DESK">
               <option value="0">SypexGeo local</option>
               <option value="1">SypexGeo REST API</option>
               <option value="2">IP Geolocation API</option>
            </field>
            <field name="weather_source_choose" type="list" default="0" label="Select weather source" description="CHOOSE_SOURCE" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">WorldWeatherOnline</option>
               <option value="1">OpenWeatherMap</option>
            </field>
            <field name="api_key" type="text" default="" label="API_KEY" description="API_KEY_DESC" showon="weather_source_choose:0" />
            <field name="api_key_sypexgeo" type="text" default="" label="SGKEY" description="SGKEY_DESK" showon="api_choose:1" />
            <field name="api_key_owm" type="text" default="" label="OPENWEATHERMAP_KEY" description="OPENWEATHERMAP_DESK" showon="weather_source_choose:1" />
            <field name="api_key_geoloc" type="text" default="" label="IPGEOLOCATION_KEY" description="IPGEOLOCATION_DESK" showon="api_choose:2" />
            <field name="api_googlemap" type="text" default="" label="GOOGLEMAP_KEY" description="GOOGLEMAP_DESC" showon="google_map:20" />
         </fieldset>
         <fieldset name="Greeting">
            <field name="greeting" type="radio" default="1" label="GREETING" description="GREETING_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="1">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="color_weather" type="color" default="#caebe4" label="COLOR_FONT" description="COLOR_FONT_DESC" />
            <field name="font_size_weather" type="text" default="90%" label="FONT_SIZE_WEATHER" description="FONT_SIZE_WEATHER_DESC" showon="google_map:0" />
            <field name="good_day" type="text" default="Good day, " label="GOOD_DAY" description="GOOD_DAY_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
            <field name="good_evening" type="text" default="Good evening, " label="GOOD_EVENING" description="GOOD_EVENING_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
            <field name="good_night" type="text" default="Good night, " label="GOOD_NIGHT" description="GOOD_NIGHT_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
            <field name="good_morning" type="text" default="Good morning, " label="GOOD_MORNING" description="GOOD_MORNING_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
            <field name="color_title" type="color" default="#e3e388" label="COLOR_FONT_GREETING" description="COLOR_FONT_GREETING_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
            <field name="font_size_title" type="text" default="110%" label="FONT_SIZE_GREETING" description="FONT_SIZE_GREETING_DESC" showon="greeting:1" />
         </fieldset>
         <fieldset name="weather_display_options">
            <field name="img" type="radio" default="1" label="DISPLAY_IMG" description="DISPLAY_IMG_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="1">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="title" type="radio" default="0" label="DISPLAY_TITLE" description="DISPLAY_TITLE_DESK" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="2">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="temp_C" type="radio" default="0" label="TEMPERC" description="TEMPERC_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="3">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="windspeedKmph" type="radio" default="0" label="WINDSPEED" description="WINDSPEED_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="4">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="pressure" type="radio" default="0" label="PRESSURE" description="PRESSURE_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="5">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="humidity" type="radio" default="0" label="HIMIDITY" description="HIMIDITY_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="6">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="cloudcover" type="radio" default="0" label="CLOUDCOVER" description="CLOUDCOVER_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="7">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="visibility" type="radio" default="0" label="VISIVILITY" description="VISIVILITY_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="8">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="weatherDesc" type="radio" default="0" label="WEATHER_IN_TWO_WORDS" description="WEATHER_DESC" class="btn-group">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="9">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field type="spacer" hr="true" />
            <field name="temp_F" type="radio" default="0" label="TEMPERF" description="TEMPERF_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="15">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="date" type="radio" default="0" label="TODAYSDATE" description="TODAYSDATE_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="14">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="sunrise" type="radio" default="0" label="SUNRISE" description="SUNRISE_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="10">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="sunset" type="radio" default="0" label="SUNSET" description="SUNSET_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="11">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="moonrise" type="radio" default="0" label="MOONRISE" description="MOONRISE_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="12">Да</option>
            </field>
            <field name="moonset" type="radio" default="0" label="MOONSET" description="MOONSET_DESC" class="btn-group" showon="weather_source_choose:0">
               <option value="0">Нет</option>
               <option value="13">Да</option>
            </field>
         </fieldset>
         <fieldset name="advanced">
            <field name="layout" type="modulelayout" label="JFIELD_ALT_LAYOUT_LABEL" description="JFIELD_ALT_MODULE_LAYOUT_DESC" />
            <field name="moduleclass_sfx" type="textarea" label="COM_MODULES_FIELD_MODULECLASS_SFX_LABEL" description="COM_MODULES_FIELD_MODULECLASS_SFX_DESC" rows="3" />
            <field name="cache" type="list" label="COM_MODULES_FIELD_CACHING_LABEL" description="COM_MODULES_FIELD_CACHING_DESC" default="1" filter="integer">
               <option value="1">JGLOBAL_USE_GLOBAL</option>
               <option value="0">COM_MODULES_FIELD_VALUE_NOCACHING</option>
            </field>
            <field name="cache_time" type="number" label="COM_MODULES_FIELD_CACHE_TIME_LABEL" description="COM_MODULES_FIELD_CACHE_TIME_DESC" default="900" filter="integer" />
            <field name="cachemode" type="hidden" default="static">
               <option value="static" />
            </field>
         </fieldset>
      </fields>
   </config>
</extension>
